data.description: So much greatness packed in one sweet home. NO CARPET throughout.  Fridge, washer and dryer convey with the home.  Wide open floor plan with natural light. Long breakfast bar perfect for entertaining guests, separate dining room that could be subbed as an office.  Large living room and guest rooms.  Oversized primary suite with walk in closet and long vanity counter for storage.  Easy to show! Check it out today!
